<!doctype html>
<html class="dark" lang="sk">
<head>
  <%- include('../components/head', { title: 'AutoSalón | Ethos' }) %>
</head>
<body class="bg-background text-on-surface" data-page="about">
<%- include('../components/header') %>

<main class="pt-40 md:pt-48 pb-24 md:pb-32">
  <section class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 mb-32 md:mb-40 text-center">
    <p class="text-primary tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-[10px] mb-8">Nocturne Drive</p>
    <h1 class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold italic tracking-tighter mb-12 leading-none">The Art of Drive</h1>
    <p class="font-headline text-xl md:text-2xl text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed italic">
      A commitment to the machine, the moment, and the movement that defines us.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="w-full mb-32 md:mb-40 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="h-[460px] md:h-[716px] w-full bg-surface-container-low relative">
      <img class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60 mix-blend-luminosity" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuA7tQpW4A42u4liUj9pa5ZEHynN2m9X5izR9rgiH6VIGfOQ0pR9prXxvKkrCVM6l8NbA0kZQwWjK4SReiNlUrmv1IF4uXBr9GmEkDuoA6b3DfQgL9s7vv7oedSnB81NhLJHkbYj46tL4v2j2bryzDZ0pt4t8q0jRMB0SCkqG-fQt9vd6lLJWhJzcycTjZb4HgYkqeI5l0EjY9pbK70mv34v8pjzWouYO9rNh8_tJHptGlgKpmA3LGWm2sxg5I4jDyEVuYxpkVQ9W" alt="Coastal road at dusk" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-surface via-surface/70 to-transparent"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 mb-40 md:mb-56 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-start">
    <div class="md:col-span-5">
      <span class="text-primary tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-[10px] mb-6 block">Mechanical Soul</span>
      <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tighter mb-8">We curate movement, not inventory.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="md:col-span-7 text-on-surface-variant text-lg leading-relaxed space-y-8 max-w-3xl">
      <p>
        Curated Motion was built as an antidote to generic automotive catalogs. We treat every vehicle as an editorial object—where provenance, texture, engineering, and restraint matter as much as outright speed.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our studio is guided by atmosphere, not urgency. We favor fewer stories, stronger curation, and the kind of quiet confidence that only craftsmanship can command.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 mb-40 md:mb-56 flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse gap-12 md:gap-20 items-start">
    <div class="md:w-[44%] w-full bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-lg overflow-hidden editorial-shadow">
      <img class="w-full aspect-[4/5] object-cover grayscale opacity-80" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuANsR7P_YGjlwm1YQJt0lhq6OzYE7WnG3hUBy7xbAJBGB1NuP4Itqz8n-JIHvM1Ts1i0BvW2iZ24S8uhXsuHy8qiSQ1QKWpEfknc4EiLyb0A0O6UAU6hcloZxpkEhW4Fnr3K9Fq8l_wOyu34l_Pw7Yp1_bY1OtKDX7G1hUiB2nYdvtvKXIZ4gwHBEU_L-TH0gQv0Rm6wB4RKd0IJLEJd7xW1QkCDPJj5lp2qA92m3nlJk6wHqHNDnWlWfJ5vY2i8m7r6OUeK2Sx" alt="The ritual" />
    </div>
    <div class="md:flex-1 space-y-10 max-w-2xl">
      <span class="text-primary tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-[10px] block">The Ritual</span>
      <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tighter leading-tight">A slower gaze. A sharper standard.</h2>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg leading-relaxed">
        We study every panel gap, every tonal reflection, every mechanical note. The goal is not volume—it is resonance. A car should feel inevitable in its presence.
      </p>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg leading-relaxed">
        This is a collection shaped by silence, precision, and the poetry of displacement. The details are not decoration; they are the reason the object endures.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="w-full bg-surface-container-low py-28 md:py-40 mb-40 md:mb-56">
    <div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="font-headline italic text-2xl md:text-4xl max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed text-on-surface">
        “Speed is merely a metric. Style is an identity. But the motion between them? That is where we live.”
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 mb-40 md:mb-56">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-16 items-start">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <span class="text-primary tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-[10px] block">Atmosphere</span>
        <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tighter">Curated to feel lived in, not launched.</h2>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Negative space, restrained typography, and images that breathe. The system is designed to feel like a gallery wall or a premium journal spread.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-surface-container-high aspect-[4/5] rounded-lg overflow-hidden relative group">
          <img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-50 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-1000" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDTbPIXjIosn_S0a4c5DGe_ulVuVv6rYEOvPbDBhemGYrKJ3OnzrBltrVu5pOiYzAg8US-7-0i_EbfRGUKV3Ro92R5eFgUCG1a3P8YJ2HgYM-fDR72ECD2pDwKqacb1h_0jZJkHno0rdky96s4hXlS7lAUIotPUEETwwvVJ-Dn2IXKaPMzdN50ebNECMD27qftsLpkqKYaer5wmM7n2o25Oc8gNTXVA9hGT5vQ4EXSMPOruLybzxiTbAxYnwfHkA41-eFxIMNkd2KVG" alt="Touch" />
          <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-8"><span class="text-[10px] tracking-widest text-primary uppercase">The Touch</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-rows-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-lg overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center p-8 md:p-12">
            <p class="font-headline italic text-xl md:text-2xl text-on-surface-variant text-center leading-relaxed">
              Every mechanical interaction should feel like a handshake between engineers.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface-container-high rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
            <img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-40" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCnMpqdh7vUtZmcG9TQtv17fOFmUbp5zcjAqwyC9GtySsgvCA1SxsqHjkSIL4pH84cM3L2tj9_yEvbJc1tE3w6iU_tbryZ1jQAhTpAXbZ6mJbTVoSxvg-3_5kIUDXG7451scvMrl9TgA0rZPd_4uCuGrHnH_2VJKy4bbKtk80i7vFg8zNbj2kvB8KTc64rpxZ6ptdsMFAO2ll-SFVuZWxI8d3LpXA9_xULpRPMM1_dBy6ldGU2MY6mp2Z14WxxdA6yIA6KqYmW4Qnll" alt="Atmospheric car" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 text-center">
    <h3 class="font-headline text-4xl font-bold tracking-tighter mb-12">Join the Movement</h3>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-8">
      <a class="group flex items-center space-x-4" href="/cars">
        <span class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-on-surface group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Visit the Showroom</span>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
      </a>
      <div class="hidden md:block w-px h-12 bg-outline-variant/30"></div>
      <a class="group flex items-center space-x-4" href="/contact">
        <span class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-on-surface group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">Contact the Atelier</span>
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('../components/footer') %>
<button id="backToTop" type="button" aria-label="Back to top">↑</button>
<script src="/assets/js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
